---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for lastseason.co.uk" canonical="/privacy/">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </section>
    <section class="section prose">
      <p>Last updated: 23 July 2026</p>
      <p>lastseason.co.uk ("we", "us") respects your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect and how we use it.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Data we collect</h2>
      <p>If you allow analytics, Google Analytics 4 receives usage information such as pages visited, interactions with fantasy tools, device category and approximate location. Analytics is not loaded before consent. We do not require an account. If you submit a daily-game score, we store the nickname you choose, a randomly generated browser identifier, puzzle date, result, number of guesses and completion time so the community leaderboard can work.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Daily games and leaderboards</h2>
      <p>Game progress, streaks, achievements, followed clubs and followed leagues are stored in your browser. Fantasy squad drafts, saved team names, player watchlists, chip ideas and checklist progress are also stored locally and are not sent to us. Community scores and fantasy team-name votes are stored in a Cloudflare D1 database. Random browser identifiers are used to limit each browser to one leaderboard entry per puzzle or one vote per name; they are not connected to an account, email address or advertising profile. Avoid using your full real name as a leaderboard nickname.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Fantasy briefing and supporter interest</h2>
      <p>If you join the fantasy briefing or supporter-interest list, we store your email address, the updates you selected, signup source and consent timestamps in Cloudflare D1. Joining the list does not create an account. We will not sell the address or start promotional delivery until a compliant email provider, sender identity and working unsubscribe process are in place. You can request deletion at any time by emailing privacy@lastseason.co.uk.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Cookies</h2>
      <p>The site stores your analytics choice in local storage under <code>lastseason-analytics-choice</code>. Saved leagues, followed clubs, recently viewed pages, game progress, fantasy plans, profile nickname and a random leaderboard identifier are also stored in your browser. Google Analytics may set cookies only after you choose “Allow analytics”. No advertising platform is currently loaded.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Third-party links</h2>
      <p>Kit pages link to third-party retailers for convenience. A retailer link may be an affiliate link only when this is disclosed beside it; in that case we may receive a commission at no extra cost to you. Third-party sites have their own privacy policies.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, or delete any personal data we hold about you. Contact us at privacy@lastseason.co.uk for any data requests.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
